summary: An ordinance relating to the improvement of Lakeside Avenue South, from a connection with Lake Washington Boulevard South, from a connection with the Lake Washington Boulevard South, south of Holgate Street, to the north line of Yesler Way produced easterly, and certain parts of certain other street and avenues, by paving, etc., as authorized by Ordinance No. 76920, creating Local Improvement District No. 5834, and amending Section 2 of said ordinance.
